            <p n="a#1">Wi Clawes Grupendale ridde<ex>re</ex> Møleke oc Gerith van der Lanken a wapn
                        gør<ex>e</ex> witerlicht oc openbar<ex>e</ex> alle the so<ex>m</ex>
